intro: Do not miss any tasks anymore and keep them in your calendar and focus on things that truly matter to you! Use it for homework or your daily routines.
description:
MeeCalendar allows you to plan and keep track of your tasks and events in a simple calendar. Add events or tasks to a day and you will not miss any important task anymore.  You can also use it to create your own daily to do list or use it for your homework assignments.
Focus on whats important and keep your mind free of dates and keep them in MeeCalendar.
